## âš¡ï¸ Why the name **Dhwaj**?

**Dhwaj (à¤§à¥à¤µà¤œ)** means *flag, banner, symbol of support or protection*.
This tool acts exactly like a protective flag â€” detecting weak/leaked API keys before attackers can exploit them.

